## Day 17 â€“ Classes and Objects

- A **class** is a blueprint/template.
- An **object** is an instance of a class.

Example:
```java
class Car {
    String name;
    void start() {
        System.out.println("Car started");
    }
}

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Car c = new Car();  // object
        c.name = "BMW";
        c.start();
    }
}
